*Područje* je prostrano. (The area is extensive.)
Ono se *područje* nalazi na jugu. (That area is located in the south.)
Ovo je vrlo značajno *područje*. (This is a very important area.)
U tome *području* ima puno šuma. (There are a lot of forests in that area.)
On je stručnjak za to *područje*. (He is an expert in that field.)